	  is invalid. [Feature #5855] [Bug #5863] [Bug #5864]

	* string.c (rb_str_concat): ditto.

	* string.c (rb_str_concat): set encoding as ASCII-8BIT when the string
	  is US-ASCII and the argument is an integer greater than 127.

